# _IN SITU_ HI-C STEP 01: CROSSLINK & STORE

This protocol is the first step in preparing your samples for _in situ_ Hi-C

---

## EQUIPMENT REQUIRED
* p-1000 pippetor
* centrifuge capable of 300G (if processing cells as opposed to tissue)

---

## SUPPLIES
1.	Sample box to hold tubes
2.	Reaction Tubes >36
3.	Razors & Forceps
4.	Gloves XL
5.	Cutting board
6.	Fine-tip sharpie
7.	Tube rocker
8.	Centrifuge able to hold tubes (able to hold temperature at 4C â€“ or spin in fridge)
9.	1mL Pipette
10.	Pipette Tips (4 boxes)
11.	Graduated Cylinder


